{"id": "art-164", "label": "Art. 164", "title": "Art. 164", "slug": "art-164", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1262648546\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1199\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1262648546\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 164 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1030196939\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1198\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1030196939\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Salariul de baz&#259; minim brut pe &#355;ar&#259;\ngarantat în plat&#259;, corespunz&#259;tor programului normal de munc&#259;, se\nstabile&#351;te anual prin hot&#259;râre a Guvernului &#351;i se aplic&#259; de\nla data de 1 ianuarie a anului urm&#259;tor, cu actualizarea periodic&#259; o\ndat&#259; pe an, dup&#259; consultarea confedera&#355;iilor sindicale &#351;i\npatronale reprezentative la nivel na&#355;ional. În cazul în care programul\nnormal de munc&#259; este, potrivit legii, mai mic de 8 ore zilnic, salariul de\nbaz&#259; minim brut orar se calculeaz&#259; prin raportarea salariului de\nbaz&#259; minim brut pe &#355;ar&#259; garantat în plat&#259; la num&#259;rul\nmediu lunar de ore, potrivit programului legal de munc&#259; aprobat.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_574985498\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1197\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_574985498\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Nivelul salariului de baz&#259; minim brut pe\n&#355;ar&#259; garantat în plat&#259;, corespunz&#259;tor programului normal de\nmunc&#259;, se stabile&#351;te &#351;i se actualizeaz&#259; potrivit\ndispozi&#355;iilor alin. (1), pe baza procedurii de aplicare a mecanismului de\nstabilire &#351;i actualizare a salariului de baz&#259; minim brut pe\n&#355;ar&#259; garantat în plat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1912383439\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1196\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1912383439\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Procedura prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (2) se\naprob&#259; prin hot&#259;râre a Guvernului, la propunerea Ministerului Muncii\n&#351;i Solidarit&#259;&#355;ii Sociale, cu consultarea Consiliului\nNa&#355;ional Tripartit pentru Dialog Social.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_406260075\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1195\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_406260075\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Procedura\nprev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (2) stabile&#351;te evaluarea gradului de adecvare\na salariului de baz&#259; minim brut pe &#355;ar&#259; garantat în plat&#259;,\nîn func&#355;ie de ponderea acestuia în câ&#351;tigul salarial mediu brut,\n&#351;i cuprinde urm&#259;toarele:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1116626633\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1194\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1116626633\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)modalit&#259;&#355;ile de stabilire &#351;i actualizare a\nnivelului salariului minim brut pe &#355;ar&#259; garantat în plat&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_46572049\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1193\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_46572049\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>criteriile de\nstabilire &#351;i actualizare ale salariului minim brut pe &#355;ar&#259;\ngarantat în plat&#259;, care s&#259; includ&#259; cel pu&#355;in\nurm&#259;toarele elemente:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_467907355\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1192\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_467907355\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(i)puterea de cump&#259;rare a salariului minim, luând în\nconsiderare costul vie&#355;ii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1109960099\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1191\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1109960099\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(ii)nivelul general al salariilor &#351;i distribu&#355;ia\nacestora;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1090174209\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1190\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1090174209\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(iii)rata de cre&#351;tere a salariilor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1198649668\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1189\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1198649668\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(iv)nivelurile &#351;i evolu&#355;iile\nproductivit&#259;&#355;ii la nivel na&#355;ional pe termen lung;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_713433796\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1188\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_713433796\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)indicatorii statistici na&#355;ionali comunica&#355;i de Institutul\nNa&#355;ional de Statistic&#259; &#351;i Comisia Na&#355;ional&#259; de\nStrategie &#351;i Prognoz&#259;, aferen&#355;i criteriilor prev&#259;zute la\nlit. b) &#351;i d);</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1319065552\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1187\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1319065552\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)setul de indicatori anuali de monitorizare &#351;i\nevaluare a impactului asupra mediului economic &#351;i social;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_117588351\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1186\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_117588351\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)modul de realizare a analizelor-suport &#351;i de\nmonitorizare a evolu&#355;iei salariului de baz&#259; minim brut pe\n&#355;ar&#259; garantat în plat&#259;, în func&#355;ie de nivelul orientativ,\nîntre 47%-52%, al ponderii valorii salariului de baz&#259; minim brut pe\n&#355;ar&#259; garantat în plat&#259; în câ&#351;tigul salarial mediu brut,\nconsiderat indicator de referin&#355;&#259; pentru evaluarea gradului de\nadecvare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_268150983\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1185\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_268150983\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Procedura prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (2) se\naplic&#259; de c&#259;tre Ministerul Muncii &#351;i Solidarit&#259;&#355;ii\nSociale, având la baz&#259; analizele unei institu&#355;ii de cercetare\nspecializate în analiza &#351;i evaluarea de impact a politicilor din domeniul\npie&#355;ei muncii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2128153115\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1184\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2128153115\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Angajatorul nu poate negocia &#351;i stabili salarii de\nbaz&#259; brute, prin contractul individual de munc&#259; &#351;i/sau\ncontractul colectiv de munc&#259; aplicabil, sub valoarea salariului de\nbaz&#259; minim brut orar, prev&#259;zut la alin. (1).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1424671614\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1183\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1424671614\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)În aplicarea prevederilor alin. (1) &#351;i (2), prin\nhot&#259;râre a Guvernului sau negocieri colective nu pot fi stabilite salarii\nminime brute sub valoarea salariului de baz&#259; minim brut pe &#355;ar&#259;\ngarantat în plat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_942873894\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1182\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_942873894\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Salariul de baz&#259; minim brut pe &#355;ar&#259;\ngarantat în plat&#259; stabilit prin hot&#259;râre a Guvernului poate fi\nacordat unui salariat pentru o perioad&#259; de maximum 24 de luni, de la data\nîncheierii contractului individual de munc&#259;. Dup&#259; expirarea perioadei\nrespective salariatului i se acord&#259; un salariu de baz&#259; superior\nsalariului de baz&#259; minim brut pe &#355;ar&#259; garantat în plat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_904171959\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1181\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_904171959\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Prin hot&#259;râre a Guvernului se poate stabili o\nmajorare a salariului de baz&#259; minim brut pe &#355;ar&#259; garantat în\nplat&#259; prev&#259;zut la alin. (1), diferen&#355;iat pe criteriile nivelului\nde studii &#351;i vechimii în munc&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_116620861\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1180\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_116620861\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Prevederile alin. (8) se aplic&#259; &#351;i în\ncazurile prev&#259;zute la alin. (9).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_310567420\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1179\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_310567420\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(11)Toate drepturile &#351;i obliga&#355;iile stabilite,\npotrivit legii, prin raportare la salariul de baz&#259; minim brut pe\n&#355;ar&#259; garantat în plat&#259; se determin&#259; utilizând nivelul\nsalariului de baz&#259; minim brut pe &#355;ar&#259; garantat în plat&#259;\nprev&#259;zut la alin. (1).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1699351675\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1178\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1699351675\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(12)Angajatorul este obligat s&#259; garanteze în\nplat&#259; salaria&#355;ilor un salariu de baz&#259; brut lunar cel pu&#355;in\negal cu salariul de baz&#259; minim brut prev&#259;zut la art. 160 alin. (3).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1912306294\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1177\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1912306294\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(13)Salariul de baz&#259; minim brut pe &#355;ar&#259;\ngarantat în plat&#259; este adus la cuno&#351;tin&#355;a salaria&#355;ilor prin\ngrija angajatorului.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}